<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.8.1">
<l>kavaḷa yāṉaik kompo citta kaṇṇa ṉeṉṟu kāma rucīrk</l>
<l>kuvaḷai mēka maṉṉa mēṉi koṇṭa kōṉeṉ ṉāṉai yeṉṟum</l>
<l>tavaḷa māṭa nīṭu nāṅkait tāma raiyāḷ kēḷva ṉeṉṟum</l>
<l>pavaḷa vāyā ḷeṉma ṭantai pārttaṉ paḷḷi pāṭu vāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying, “Kaṇṇaṉ who broke the tusk of the elephant in musth,”</l>
<l>Saying, “My elephant, king with a body like a cloud and a blue lily</l>
<l rend="indent">of desirable quality,”</l>
<l>And saying, “The lotus lady’s lover of spacious Nāṅkai with white mansions,”</l>
<l>The coral-lipped one, my girl sings of Pārttaṉpaḷḷi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
